East of Middlegate, the paths of the Pony Express, Lincoln Highway and US&nbsp;50 diverge, using different passes to cross the Desatoya Mountains. They rejoin west of Austin, Nevada Austin. The first paved route of the Lincoln Highway is preserved as Nevada State Route 722 State Route 722.
